                    <h2 id="other-nih-agencies" class="__title visible">Other NIH Agencies</h2>
                    </div>

  
  <p>Elsewhere at NIH, <strong>the National Institute of Environmental Health Sciences (NIEHS) received $10 </strong><strong>million in funding in the emergency supplemental package, but no details are available yet on </strong><strong>how this funding will be awarded</strong>. We also anticipate that, in the coming weeks and months, additional Institutes and Centers will be issuing opportunities for administrative supplements for research on COVID-19 that is related to their underlying programmatic priorities. We will share such at information as it becomes available.</p>



  
